  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CustomConfiguredUI.IAuthenticationSuccessful  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomConfiguredUI
    A UI encapsulating all other specific UIs in this application so that child UIs don't have to bother with the same old routines of setting everything up.
    CustomConfiguredUI.AppServlet
    A single servlet to serve all content of this application, whether static or dynamic.
    CustomConfiguredUIServlet  
    UniversalUIExtension
    A special extension to UI that enables logging client issues on the server and some other things.
    UserAuth
    A utility class that manages information about the currently logged-in user.
    UserSession
    A utility class that manages all attributes the application stores in user sessions.
    UserUploads
    A class wrapping multi file-upload functionality for a single user - an instance of this class is exclusively mapped to a particular session.

    Public definition of all used UIs.
